1812if(copy_AlgorithmIdentifier(&((from)->supportedCMSTypes)->val[((to)->supportedCMSTypes)->len], &((to)->supportedCMSTypes)->val[((to)->supportedCMSTypes)->len])) goto fail;
1813}

5231ret = 0;
5232ret += der_length_octet_string(&(data)->pk_as_rep);
5233ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
5234ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
5235ret += Top_tag_oldret;
5236}
5237{
5238size_t Top_tag_oldret = ret;
5239ret = 0;
5240ret += length_Ticket(&(data)->ticket);
5241ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
5242ret += Top_tag_oldret;
5243}
5244ret += 1 + der_length_len (ret);
5245return ret;
5246}

5248int ASN1CALL
5249copy_PkinitSuppPubInfo(const PkinitSuppPubInfo *from, PkinitSuppPubInfo *to)
5250{
5251memset(to, 0, sizeof(*to));
5252*(&(to)->enctype) = *(&(from)->enctype);
5253if(der_copy_octet_string(&(from)->as_REQ, &(to)->as_REQ)) goto fail;
5254if(der_copy_octet_string(&(from)->pk_as_rep, &(to)->pk_as_rep)) goto fail;
5255if(copy_Ticket(&(from)->ticket, &(to)->ticket)) goto fail;
5256return 0;
5257fail:
5258free_PkinitSuppPubInfo(to);
5259return ENOMEM;
5260}
